---------------------------------------------------------------------------
CCK LIVE FIELD PLUGIN FOR SEBLOD 2.X CCK FOR JOOMLA 1.7.X AND JOOMLA 2.1.X
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 1.0.0
Name: SD Live CCK Field
Author: Simon Dowdles - www.onestuckpixel.com
Twitter: @simondowdles

--------------
Description
--------------

Use the value of any CCK field in the main article within the page and set it as a live value on any field

--------------
Instructions
--------------

> Install

> Go to the content type / search type's field type you want to set a live value on

> Select live type SD CCK Field and specify the field_name as the value

> The value of field_name will be used as the live value where field_name is an existing field name of the main content type
 
